   "source": [
    "# Data Cleaning and Combination\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook combines multiple datasets:\n",
    "- cleaned_real_estate_data.csv (main dataset)\n",
    "- CT_school_data.csv (school rankings by city)\n",
    "- uszips.csv (zip code to city mapping)\n",
    "- DECENNIALSF22010.PCT15 (census data by zip code)\n",
    "- Connecticut_DemographicsByCity_sample.csv (population data by city)"
   ]
  },
  {
